      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Roan Mountain Highlands</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Roan Gebirgshochländer</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Montagnes de Montagne de Roan</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Highlands Da Montanha De Roan</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Altopiani Della Montagna Di Roan</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Roan ορεινές περιοχές βουνών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Montañas De la Montaña De Roan</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This Carolina Environmental Diversity Explorations "virtual field trip" explores the natural beauty and geological and ecological diversity of the Roan Mountain Highlands that straddle the border between North Carolina and Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Carolina virtuellen, welches die 
Klimaverschiedenartigkeit-Erforschungen "Reise" auffangen, 
erforscht die natürliche Schönheit und die geologische und 
ökologische Verschiedenartigkeit der Roan Gebirgshochländer, die den
Rand zwischen Nord-Carolina und Tennessee spreizen.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les explorations environnementales "voyage de 
cette diversité de la Caroline de zone virtuel" explore la beauté 
normale et la diversité géologique et écologique des montagnes de 
montagne de Roan qui écartent les jambes le cadre entre la Caroline 
du nord et le Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">As explorações ambientais "desengate desta 
diversidade de Carolina de campo virtual" exploram a beleza natural e 
a diversidade geological e ecological dos highlands da montanha de 
Roan que escarrancham a beira entre North.carolina e Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le esplorazioni ambientali "viaggio di questa 
diversità della Carolina di campo virtuale" esplora la bellezza 
naturale e la diversità geologica ed ecologica degli altopiani della 
montagna di Roan che cavalcano il bordo fra North.carolina ed il 
Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εξερευνήσεις "εικονικό ταξίδι αυτής της 
ποικιλομορφίας της Καρολίνας οι περιβαλλοντικές πεδίων" ερευνούν 
τη φυσική ομορφιά και τη γεωλογική και οικολογική ποικιλομορφία 
των roan ορεινών περιοχών βουνών που καβαλικεύουν τα σύνορα 
μεταξύ της βόρειας Καρολίνας και του Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Las exploraciones ambientales "disparo al campo de
esta diversidad de Carolina virtual" exploran la belleza natural y la 
diversidad geológica y ecológica de las montañas de la montaña de 
Roan que montan la frontera a horcajadas entre Carolina del Norte y 
Tennessee.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wissenschaft und Technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La Science et technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciência e tecnologia</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencia y tecnología</string>
          </keyword>
